\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 We have a silly lie where I come from. We believe the cold makes us tough instilling in us a resilience as enduring as the permafrost and a work ethic like the steadfast pines under snow.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 It doesn\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t, really. }
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 It\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s a gentle deception, a lullaby, an anthem.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 All lies are intended to make us feel more comfortable and safe. We drape it around our shoulders against a bitter cold.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\pard\plain \sa180\sb180\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0 Lies are tender guardians, they cradle you in a familiar embrace. I hope you find your roots there, flourish and thrive, nurtured in the soil of what you know.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 That you believe in.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Truth on the other hand, truth is a traveling companion. One who teases you with a letter from a foreign country, one that whispers from }{\f1\fs20\b0\i0 beyond the threshold of the known, where the soul ventures forth in search of something more profound than the lulling serenity of the familiar.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 It is the voice of the sea, a shout big a strong, screaming and screaming. And the thing it is screaming is, yoooou... with shit instead of brains... life is immense... can you understand that?}{ }
\par\pard\plain \sa180\sb180\ltrch\loch {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 The truth may travel it may even grow, but it is unchanging.}
\par\pard\plain \ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0 I\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92ve often thought about the balance of these two forces in our lives \endash  like watching the northern lights that your Morfor so dearly wanted to see, a mesmerizing dance of light and darkness.}{ }
\par\pard\plain \sa180\sb180\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0 Lies and truths. We learn, we grow, and we find solace in knowing that both have their rightful place in the vast landscape of our existence.}
\par\pard\plain \sa180\sb180\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Like anything in life it depends on your perspective }{\f1\fs20\b0\i0 And that's where you have your own superpowers. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 For many people that flag represented Peace. Good people who had hope in their hearts and a kind of humble optimism that they were earnestly bursting to share with the world. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 But I never saw that in my lifetime. [switch camera angles]}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 The mythology we inherit depends on which side you\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92re on.}
\par\pard\plain \sa180\sb180\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0 Even though I was not there to watch you grow, know that you have always been in my heart, a constant presence that no border could ever diminish.  }
