\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\pard\plain \ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0 \line They will raise you to think like them to love it there.\line \line They will tell you to worship that flag in school\line \line But you don't have to. In my view. You are not one of them\line You have a choice and you are part of a different community\line The human community.\line \line You are welcome here. \line \line From my perspective you were stolen from that community. And you are always welcome back. But you have to fight for that yourself. And against the psychotic selfishness of that place that stole you from me.\line \line It's all about perspective. And that's where you have your own superpowers. }
